表格工资结构配置的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('SalaryConfig')
and type = 'U')
drop table SalaryConfig
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: SalaryConfig */
/*==============================================================*/
create table SalaryConfig (
ID integer identity,
WorkType varchar(50) null,
WorkDesc varchar(50) null,
Level integer null,
LevelDesc varchar(50) null,
MoneyPreHour decimal(8,2) null
)
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'1：注塑
2：植毛
3：包装
4：夹具
5：其它',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'SalaryConfig', 'column', 'WorkType'
go
